# ============================================
# META PLATFORMS (Facebook, Instagram, Threads)
# ============================================
# How to get credentials:
# 1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/
# 2. Create a new app
# 3. Add required permissions (pages_manage_posts, instagram_basic, threads_basic, etc.)
# 4. Generate a long-lived user access token
# 5. Get your Page ID, Instagram Account ID, and Threads User ID

# Shared Meta Access Token (works for all Meta platforms)
